29namespace webrtc {
30
31// Extends StreamStatistician with methods needed by the implementation.
32class StreamStatisticianImplInterface : public StreamStatistician {
33 public:
34 virtual ~StreamStatisticianImplInterface() = default;
35 virtual void MaybeAppendReportBlockAndReset(
36 std::vector<rtcp::ReportBlock>& report_blocks) = 0;
37 virtual void SetMaxReorderingThreshold(int max_reordering_threshold) = 0;
38 virtual void EnableRetransmitDetection(bool enable) = 0;
39 virtual void UpdateCounters(const RtpPacketReceived& packet) = 0;
40};
41
42// Thread-compatible implementation of StreamStatisticianImplInterface.
43class StreamStatisticianImpl : public StreamStatisticianImplInterface {
44 public:
45 StreamStatisticianImpl(uint32_t ssrc,
46 Clock* clock,
47 int max_reordering_threshold);
48 ~StreamStatisticianImpl() override;
49
50 // Implements StreamStatistician
51 RtpReceiveStats GetStats() const override;
52 absl::optional<int> GetFractionLostInPercent() const override;
53 StreamDataCounters GetReceiveStreamDataCounters() const override;
54 uint32_t BitrateReceived() const override;
55
56 // Implements StreamStatisticianImplInterface
57 void MaybeAppendReportBlockAndReset(
58 std::vector<rtcp::ReportBlock>& report_blocks) override;
59 void SetMaxReorderingThreshold(int max_reordering_threshold) override;
60 void EnableRetransmitDetection(bool enable) override;
61 // Updates StreamStatistician for incoming packets.
62 void UpdateCounters(const RtpPacketReceived& packet) override;
63
64 private:
65 bool IsRetransmitOfOldPacket(const RtpPacketReceived& packet,
66 int64_t now_ms) const;
67 void UpdateJitter(const RtpPacketReceived& packet, int64_t receive_time_ms);
68 // Updates StreamStatistician for out of order packets.
69 // Returns true if packet considered to be out of order.
70 bool UpdateOutOfOrder(const RtpPacketReceived& packet,
71 int64_t sequence_number,
72 int64_t now_ms);
73 // Checks if this StreamStatistician received any rtp packets.
74 bool ReceivedRtpPacket() const { return received_seq_first_ >= 0; }
75
76 const uint32_t ssrc_;
77 Clock* const clock_;
78 // Delta used to map internal timestamps to Unix epoch ones.
79 const int64_t delta_internal_unix_epoch_ms_;
80 RateStatistics incoming_bitrate_;
81 // In number of packets or sequence numbers.
82 int max_reordering_threshold_;
83 bool enable_retransmit_detection_;
84 bool cumulative_loss_is_capped_;
85
86 // Stats on received RTP packets.
87 uint32_t jitter_q4_;
88 // Cumulative loss according to RFC 3550, which may be negative (and often is,
89 // if packets are reordered and there are non-RTX retransmissions).
90 int32_t cumulative_loss_;
91 // Offset added to outgoing rtcp reports, to make ensure that the reported
92 // cumulative loss is non-negative. Reports with negative values confuse some
93 // senders, in particular, our own loss-based bandwidth estimator.
94 int32_t cumulative_loss_rtcp_offset_;
95
96 int64_t last_receive_time_ms_;
97 uint32_t last_received_timestamp_;
98 SequenceNumberUnwrapper seq_unwrapper_;
99 int64_t received_seq_first_;
100 int64_t received_seq_max_;
101 // Assume that the other side restarted when there are two sequential packets
102 // with large jump from received_seq_max_.
103 absl::optional<uint16_t> received_seq_out_of_order_;
104
105 // Current counter values.
106 StreamDataCounters receive_counters_;
107
108 // Counter values when we sent the last report.
109 int32_t last_report_cumulative_loss_;
110 int64_t last_report_seq_max_;
111};
112
113// Thread-safe implementation of StreamStatisticianImplInterface.
114class StreamStatisticianLocked : public StreamStatisticianImplInterface {
115 public:
116 StreamStatisticianLocked(uint32_t ssrc,
117 Clock* clock,
118 int max_reordering_threshold)
119 : impl_(ssrc, clock, max_reordering_threshold) {}
120 ~StreamStatisticianLocked() override = default;
121
122 RtpReceiveStats GetStats() const override {
123 MutexLock lock(&stream_lock_);
124 return impl_.GetStats();
125 }
126 absl::optional<int> GetFractionLostInPercent() const override {
127 MutexLock lock(&stream_lock_);
128 return impl_.GetFractionLostInPercent();
129 }
130 StreamDataCounters GetReceiveStreamDataCounters() const override {
131 MutexLock lock(&stream_lock_);
132 return impl_.GetReceiveStreamDataCounters();
133 }
134 uint32_t BitrateReceived() const override {
135 MutexLock lock(&stream_lock_);
136 return impl_.BitrateReceived();
137 }
138 void MaybeAppendReportBlockAndReset(
139 std::vector<rtcp::ReportBlock>& report_blocks) override {
140 MutexLock lock(&stream_lock_);
141 impl_.MaybeAppendReportBlockAndReset(report_blocks);
142 }
143 void SetMaxReorderingThreshold(int max_reordering_threshold) override {
144 MutexLock lock(&stream_lock_);
145 return impl_.SetMaxReorderingThreshold(max_reordering_threshold);
146 }
147 void EnableRetransmitDetection(bool enable) override {
148 MutexLock lock(&stream_lock_);
149 return impl_.EnableRetransmitDetection(enable);
150 }
151 void UpdateCounters(const RtpPacketReceived& packet) override {
152 MutexLock lock(&stream_lock_);
153 return impl_.UpdateCounters(packet);
154 }
155
156 private:
157 mutable Mutex stream_lock_;
158 StreamStatisticianImpl impl_ RTC_GUARDED_BY(&stream_lock_);
159};
160
161// Thread-compatible implementation.
162class ReceiveStatisticsImpl : public ReceiveStatistics {
163 public:
164 ReceiveStatisticsImpl(
165 Clock* clock,
166 std::function<std::unique_ptr<StreamStatisticianImplInterface>(
167 uint32_t ssrc,
168 Clock* clock,
169 int max_reordering_threshold)> stream_statistician_factory);
170 ~ReceiveStatisticsImpl() override = default;
171
172 // Implements ReceiveStatisticsProvider.
173 std::vector<rtcp::ReportBlock> RtcpReportBlocks(size_t max_blocks) override;
174
175 // Implements RtpPacketSinkInterface
176 void OnRtpPacket(const RtpPacketReceived& packet) override;
177
178 // Implements ReceiveStatistics.
179 StreamStatistician* GetStatistician(uint32_t ssrc) const override;
180 void SetMaxReorderingThreshold(int max_reordering_threshold) override;
181 void SetMaxReorderingThreshold(uint32_t ssrc,
182 int max_reordering_threshold) override;
183 void EnableRetransmitDetection(uint32_t ssrc, bool enable) override;
184
185 private:
186 StreamStatisticianImplInterface* GetOrCreateStatistician(uint32_t ssrc);
187
188 Clock* const clock_;
189 std::function<std::unique_ptr<StreamStatisticianImplInterface>(
190 uint32_t ssrc,
191 Clock* clock,
192 int max_reordering_threshold)>
193 stream_statistician_factory_;
194 // The index within `all_ssrcs_` that was last returned.
195 size_t last_returned_ssrc_idx_;
196 std::vector<uint32_t> all_ssrcs_;
197 int max_reordering_threshold_;
198 std::unordered_map<uint32_t /*ssrc*/,
199 std::unique_ptr<StreamStatisticianImplInterface>>
200 statisticians_;
201};
202
203// Thread-safe implementation wrapping access to ReceiveStatisticsImpl with a
204// mutex.
205class ReceiveStatisticsLocked : public ReceiveStatistics {
206 public:
207 explicit ReceiveStatisticsLocked(
208 Clock* clock,
209 std::function<std::unique_ptr<StreamStatisticianImplInterface>(
210 uint32_t ssrc,
211 Clock* clock,
212 int max_reordering_threshold)> stream_statitician_factory)
213 : impl_(clock, std::move(stream_statitician_factory)) {}
214 ~ReceiveStatisticsLocked() override = default;
215 std::vector<rtcp::ReportBlock> RtcpReportBlocks(size_t max_blocks) override {
216 MutexLock lock(&receive_statistics_lock_);
217 return impl_.RtcpReportBlocks(max_blocks);
218 }
219 void OnRtpPacket(const RtpPacketReceived& packet) override {
220 MutexLock lock(&receive_statistics_lock_);
221 return impl_.OnRtpPacket(packet);
222 }
223 StreamStatistician* GetStatistician(uint32_t ssrc) const override {
224 MutexLock lock(&receive_statistics_lock_);
225 return impl_.GetStatistician(ssrc);
226 }
227 void SetMaxReorderingThreshold(int max_reordering_threshold) override {
228 MutexLock lock(&receive_statistics_lock_);
229 return impl_.SetMaxReorderingThreshold(max_reordering_threshold);
230 }
231 void SetMaxReorderingThreshold(uint32_t ssrc,
232 int max_reordering_threshold) override {
233 MutexLock lock(&receive_statistics_lock_);
234 return impl_.SetMaxReorderingThreshold(ssrc, max_reordering_threshold);
235 }
236 void EnableRetransmitDetection(uint32_t ssrc, bool enable) override {
237 MutexLock lock(&receive_statistics_lock_);
238 return impl_.EnableRetransmitDetection(ssrc, enable);
239 }
240
241 private:
242 mutable Mutex receive_statistics_lock_;
243 ReceiveStatisticsImpl impl_ RTC_GUARDED_BY(&receive_statistics_lock_);
244};
245
246} // namespace webrtc
